Decription should be editable
Make, Model, Year should be editable
Engine, Tranmission, SOP number should be editable
Last Modified by, Last Modified Date should be read only should display '(System Generated)'
2. When Editing new record :
Estimate  should be read only
Vehicle series should be read only
Number of vehicle should be editable
Decription should be read only
Make, Model, Year should be read only
Engine, Tranmission, SOP number should be read only
Last Modified by, Last Modified Date should be read only 
